=Configure Patches Window: Interface Section=
[[File:en/Patches-interface.png|center|1. - The Configure patches window; Interface]]

====Show vehicle speed in status bar====
Whether or not the vehicle speed is shown in the vehicle window status bar, where you can stop or make a train go.

====Always show long date in status bar====
When on show the full date all the time rather than just in pause mode.

====Show finances window at the end of the year====
Whether or not the finances window is shown at the end of the year.

====Pan window when mouse is at the edge====
When the mouse is at the edge of the window the view will scroll when this is on.

====Duration of error messages====
How long error messages are shown for in seconds.